    class DummyGlobeAnnotation
extends gov.nasa.worldwind.render.GlobeAnnotation
    Dummy non-serializable superclass that provides a no-arg constructor that is needed by the serialization process of a serializable subclass in order to initialize a non-serializable superclass.

    Stephen Wong
